OL,5, Transport campaigners have welcomed a  
OL,6, temporary sale on train tickets across 
OL,7, the UK, but argue that costs should be 
OL,8, cut even further.                      
OL,10,FThe government's "Great British Rail   
OL,11,FSale" will see prices slashed by as    
OL,12,Fmuch as half, with cheaper off-peak    
OL,13,Ftravel on offer in April and May.      
OL,15,FBut the Campaign for Better Transport  
OL,16,Fsaid wider price increases are "driving
OL,17,Fpeople off the railway".               
OL,19,FPassenger numbers on trains have not   
OL,20,Fyet returned to pre-pandemic levels.   
